<h1>HOW DO I UPDATE MY BILLING AND/OR SHIPPING INFORMATION?</h1>
<p>Updating or changing your billing and shipping information is super easy.</p>
<p>If you are a ‘Gift’ or ‘I want to pay “Once” subscriber, send us an email with your new address at  <a href="mailto:talktous@creoroom.com">talktous@creoroom.com</a> and we’ll send you a confirmation about your address update or change.</p>
<p>If you are an ‘ I want to pay “Monthly” subscriber, open any email sent to you by CREO, find the link that reads ‘Update/Change your billing/shipping information’ at the bottom of the email, enter the email address and password you signed up with and you’re done.
